GEOLOGY: Study of rock, minerals, and terrain

Category: Science
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Understanding rock formations, mineral deposits, and the structure of
the earth. Useful for prospecting, mining, judging whether a cave
system or rift-scarred terrain is stable, and recognizing valuable
ore or stone on sight.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, astronomy, archaeology
